properties.Name: CustomerAccountStatusType
properties.Description:
A type of status that may be associated with a  Customer Account for a period of time.

Ex:
- Active
- Current
- Dormant
- Blocked
- Exceeds requirements
- Needs to be funded
- Closed
- Inactive
- Frozen
- Collection Suspended
- Suspended
- Delinquent
- In Default
- Unknown
